Class ContactTest.Contact

  • java.lang.Object
    • ContactTest.Contact
  • Enclosing class:
    ContactTest

    public static class ContactTest.Contact
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Jack Protivnak This class will be fed information from the user input and will then run it through an input validation within a method to test its characters. It will then tell the user if they entered an invalid character or it will continue. It also contains methods for returning the data.
